<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>생명과 사회 모의고사 (7~11주차)</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2c3e50;
            --secondary-color: #34495e;
            --accent-color: #3498db;
            --bg-color: #f8f9fa;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-color: #333333;
            --border-color: #e0e0e0;
            --correct-color: #27ae60;
            --incorrect-color: #c0392b;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--primary-color);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        header h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        header p {
            color: #666;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .quiz-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .question-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .question-num {
            background: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .options-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        }

        .option-item {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .option-label {
            display: block;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            background: #fdfdfd;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .option-label:hover {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        .option-item input[type="radio"] {
            margin-right: 10px;
            accent-color: var(--accent-color);
        }

        .explanation-box {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #94a3b8;
        }

        .option-item.correct .option-label {
            background-color: #e8f5e9 !important;
            border-color: var(--correct-color) !important;
            color: var(--correct-color);
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .option-item.incorrect .option-label {
            background-color: #ffebee !important;
            border-color: var(--incorrect-color) !important;
            color: var(--incorrect-color);
        }

        .submit-btn-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .action-btn {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .action-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .score-board {
            display: none;
            background: #ebf5fb;
            border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
